belongs_to_collection.name: The Gabriels: Election Year in the Life of One Family

overview: Back in the kitchen of the Gabriel family, the country is now in the midst of the general election for President. In the course of one evening in the house they grew up in, history (both theirs and our country's), money, politics, family, art and culture are chopped up and mixed together, while a meal is made around the kitchen table.
title: What Did You Expect?
